                            <div class="muscle-text exercise-equipment-start">
                                <h3><strong>Single Pulley Tower</strong></h3><p><span data-sheets-root="1" data-sheets-value="{&quot;1&quot;:2,&quot;2&quot;:&quot;This is a smaller cable machine option that take up less space. It can be used with a wide range of attachments.&quot;}" data-sheets-userformat="{&quot;2&quot;:15233,&quot;3&quot;:{&quot;1&quot;:0},&quot;10&quot;:2,&quot;11&quot;:0,&quot;12&quot;:0,&quot;14&quot;:{&quot;1&quot;:2,&quot;2&quot;:0},&quot;15&quot;:&quot;Calibri, sans-serif&quot;,&quot;16&quot;:11}">This is a smaller cable machine option that takes up less space. It can be used with a wide range of attachments.</span></p><h3><strong>Straight Bar Attachment</strong></h3><p><span data-sheets-root="1" data-sheets-value="{&quot;1&quot;:2,&quot;2&quot;:&quot;This easily attaches to a cable machine and can be used for a wide variety of arm exercises. Ensure your hands are in the correct position to limit wrist stress.&quot;}" data-sheets-userformat="{&quot;2&quot;:15233,&quot;3&quot;:{&quot;1&quot;:0},&quot;10&quot;:2,&quot;11&quot;:0,&quot;12&quot;:0,&quot;14&quot;:{&quot;1&quot;:2,&quot;2&quot;:0},&quot;15&quot;:&quot;Calibri, sans-serif&quot;,&quot;16&quot;:11}">This easily attaches to a cable machine and can be used for a wide variety of arm exercises. Ensure your hands are in the correct position to limit wrist stress.</span></p>                            </div>
